Parliament, Tuesday, 27 March 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Higher Education will today undertake an oversight visit to the Cape Peninsula University of Technology (CPUT), Bellville Campus. Details are as follows: 
	
	Date: 28 March 2018
	Time: 09:00 am
	Venue: CPUT Bellville Campus ISSUED BY PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON HIGHER EDUCATION, MS CONNIE SEPTEMBER For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Mava Lukani (Mr)
